Revision history for Mason-Plugin-PSGIHandler

** denotes an incompatible change

0.06  Mar 10, 2011

- Require Plack 0.9910, tests won't pass before that

0.05  Mar 7, 2011

- Specify is=>'ro' explicitly; MooseX::HasDefaults only seems to transfer from base class some of the time

0.04  Mar 6, 2011

- Use new Mason 2.05 default file extensions in tests

0.03  Feb 27, 2011

- Depend on File::Path, and use mkpath rather than make_path for better compatibility (Tomohiro Hosaka)

0.02  Feb 24, 2011

- Fix reference to cmeta->args

0.01  Feb 16, 2011

- Initial version

